{"tid":1011965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男童放煙花不慎炸穿女子耳膜　家長：唔係我個仔做！","createTime":"2019-02-07T07:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T10:57:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b14a092b8d3bdbe07d2496597d3019a1b9aedd","tid":1011965,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:50:23.000Z","msg":"重慶合川區一名林姓女子，周日（3日）晚在當地雲門鎮廣場遊玩，期間目睹兩個男童施放名為「沖天炮」的煙花，林女疑走避不及，遭該炮炸穿右耳耳膜。有男童事後承認自己燃放煙花不慎，擊中林女頭部；惟其家長則稱，煙花並非孩子所燃放。目前林女已報案，當地警方正介入調查。<br />\n「沖天炮就打到耳朵這裏，耳朵還流血了，很多炸藥的渣滓散在頭髮上面，我耳朵當時就聽不見了。」林女憶述時猶有餘悸，她的右耳耳膜被擊穿、破裂，聽力受到影響，須在合川區人民醫院耳鼻喉科病房留醫。<br />\n林女表示，當時她和朋友在廣場玩耍，兩名男童在廣場一角燃放沖天炮，其中一枚煙花正好在林女腳邊炸響。林女閃避期間，其耳朵附近被一枚沖天炮擊中。她現在說話時頭部仍發痛，右耳處於失聰狀態，「我的耳膜裏破裂了個洞，耳朵痛，吞嚥東西會陣痛，現在說話這邊聽不清楚，就像有東西蓋在上面一樣」。<br />\n當日燃放煙花的男童承認錯誤，「我們耍沖天炮，我們把它點起，就衝到這個姊姊那裏了，就把姊姊的耳朵炸了」。林女提到，自己住院花費有數千元人民幣，與男童家長協商時，對方否認自家孩子燃放煙花，反指是其他小孩造成，已報案處理，要求警方調查。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190207/photo/bkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001_01b.jpg?20190207130953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001_01b.jpg%3F20190207130953&h=3623f88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190207/photo/bkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001_02b.jpg?20190207130953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20190207130953&h=6e3d51a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190207/photo/bkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001_03b.jpg?20190207130953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001_03b.jpg%3F20190207130953&h=ef183481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190207/photo/bkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001_04b.jpg?20190207130953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001_04b.jpg%3F20190207130953&h=de0003f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190207/bkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190207%2Fbkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001.html&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYBA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=3e8c23e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190207/bkn-20190207025615566-0207_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ea2e25c2cd9b576e6c0147dc3a2fac2c7b51eef6","tid":1011965,"uid":200328,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"支那家長無論咩情況都只會答兩句野<br />\n唔係我個仔做<br />\n他只是個孩子啊"},{"pid":"a3997bd5564f0e276569b400ae384943c31eadb0","tid":1011965,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"不嬲都覺得呢d 俾人玩既煙花好危險<br />\n就算你冇玩都隨時俾人射到<br />\n而家會選擇性咁遠離呢d 玩煙花既地方"},{"pid":"edb81e9f157b1d26eb555efad69d75512054445d","tid":1011965,"uid":58374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"啲大陸婆不嬲拎個西出嚟生仔就算<br />\n唔會教唔會睇"},{"pid":"adfff0b36c92a90f49bcc042b3c6074612e7c86d","tid":1011965,"uid":42188,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/230020_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F230020_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=569ba574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fea4b70d0dd2e3b7ae579d438922bcbd5f6b3f5","tid":1011965,"uid":140606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:01:24.000Z","msg":"屯門元朗上水一帶仲有好多人玩<br />\n好近民居好危險"},{"pid":"69e4011f72812317d239187e776d8f9561950e72","tid":10119